description: Lists proficiencies associated with a user.

parameters.name: InstanceId
parameters.description: The identifier of the Amazon Connect instance. You can find the instance ID in the Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the instance.

parameters.name: UserId
parameters.description: The identifier of the user account.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: If there are additional results, this is the token for the next set of results.

nested_items.name: AttributeName
nested_items.description: The name of user's proficiency. You must use name of predefined attribute present in the Amazon Connect instance.

nested_items.name: AttributeValue
nested_items.description: The value of user's proficiency. You must use value of predefined attribute present in the Amazon Connect instance.

nested_items.name: Level
nested_items.description: The level of the proficiency. The valid values are 1, 2, 3, 4 and 5.

nested_items.name: LastModifiedTime
nested_items.description: The last time that the user's proficiencies are were modified.

nested_items.name: LastModifiedRegion
nested_items.description: The region in which a user's proficiencies were last modified.
